BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA June 17 -- Ambassador of the Democratic 
People's Republic of Korea Han Min-chol held here yesterday a 
press conference to introduce the DPRK Foreign Ministry's 
statement dated June 13 on the nuclear issue of his country. 
  At the function, Ambassador Han Min-chol informed the 
participants of the DPRK's withdrawal from the International 
Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) and affirmed that this issue can 
only be resolved properly through negotiations and consultation. 

